{"tid":2495790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】今晚荃灣兩棟大廈封區強檢","createTime":"2021-04-19T11:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T11:36:46.000Z","uid":333287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fbc1bfc2d9ec788482057872bd568cd95afd043c","tid":2495790,"uid":333287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:36:46.000Z","msg":"本報收到可靠消息，今晚（4月19日）8點政府將對荃灣兩處住宅樓宇進行封區強檢。<br />\n<br />\n一處，是位於青山公路荃灣段620號的麗城花園第二期第4座，住宅樓層4至41樓，合共304個單位，1989年10月入伙。<br />\n<br />\n另一棟是位於荃灣芙蓉街的芙蓉大廈<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2021-04-19/68642525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2021-04-19%2F68642525&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=6b3288e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2021-04-19/68642525</a>"}]}